{"type":"text","timestamp":1775884976473,"sessionID":"ses_28502d4deffeN9iJueUE2C5tWU","part":{"id":"prt_d7afe3cfc001Uj6x0KF0HjO7Ay","messageID":"msg_d7afe1407001iuIufcQKtU4jrX","sessionID":"ses_28502d4deffeN9iJueUE2C5tWU","type":"text","text":"Now I understand the task. I need to write a comprehensive design.md for AR-020 (CLI pack command) in the changes/AR-020 directory. Based on the specs provided, I'll create a detailed technical design document.","time":{"start":1775884976471,"end":1775884976471}}}
