{"type":"text","timestamp":1775885266974,"sessionID":"ses_28502d4deffeN9iJueUE2C5tWU","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0291dc001uFaqTOzwrkT81J","messageID":"msg_d7b019e7f001jeOG0ok4TXj9Go","sessionID":"ses_28502d4deffeN9iJueUE2C5tWU","type":"text","text":"I've successfully created the `design.md` file for the AR-020 CLI pack command at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/design.md`.\n\nThe design document includes:\n\n**Structure (961 lines):**\n1. **Overview** - AR ID, module (cmd/cli), language (Python), size (M)\n2. **Architecture** - High-level and component architecture diagrams\n3. **Package Layout** - Complete file structure with roles\n4. **Console Script Entry Point** - TOML configuration and Typer app setup\n5. **Typer Root Callback** - Global options with version and verbose\n6. **Typer `pack` Command** - Full command signature with all options\n7. **Helper Functions** - `version_callback` and `_handle_error`\n8. **`PackRuntime` Class** - All 17 methods with detailed docstrings\n9. **`MetadataService` Class** - Load, save, update, validate operations\n10. **Data Models** - `AgentMetadata` (Pydantic) and `MetadataOptions` (dataclass)\n11. **Dependencies** - Required and optional dependencies in pyproject.toml format\n12. **Module Exports** - `__init__.py` exports for agentcube and runtime packages\n13. **Workflow Diagram** - ASCII flow diagram of pack execution\n14. **Error Handling** - Exception hierarchy and error scenarios table\n15. **Implementation Notes** - Key implementation details","time":{"start":1775885266973,"end":1775885266973}}}
